{
  "stem": "18932.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 470.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But all my aunt-- my-- all my aunts and uncles and my grandmother and grandfather was evacuated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Did you ever see them again?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we never-- no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We heard that they were taken to [NON-ENGLISH], and I think they were executed there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess because I didn't look Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had blue eyes, and I had red hair.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, next we just unpacked everything again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother, before we would-- ready to-- she left the window open because my father wasn't home, and so this way he could come back and take out the stuff that she hid in the stove.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then so we-- we went back in, and we just stood on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, I didn't have any cousins.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had one cousin, which this cousin left for the United States before the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, other cousins, there were some were in Israel and some were in a different town.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They did not live-- all of them did not live in-- in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The next time, there was-- we were supposed to leave our home, and we were supposed to go into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that time, my father came back, and we packed everything, whatever little we could, and we marched with everybody else into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, he was doing business.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was still doing business during the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He would take off the Jewish star, and he would go and do-- conduct business.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a yellow-- like a Magen David, like a Jewish star.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And inside there was written in black, Jude, what means Jew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You-- you-- you bought them, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I can't remember now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really don't remember that much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to sew it on ourselves.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
